dct_title_s: Natural Gas Underground Storage Facilities, United States, 2014
dct_description_sm: This point shapefile represents underground natural gas storage fields in the United States as of July 2014. County centroids are used for map location. These data were gathered from EIA-191, Monthly Underground Gas Storage Report. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data produced by the U.S. National Energy Information Administration.

This dataset is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
